Installation Instructions
*************************

Currently only the firefox branch is maintained.

Steps for installation:

1. Pack the contents of the folder "firefox" into a ZIP archive
   and name this archive flvideoreplacer@trupf.xpi

   Example command line for Linux:

   cd firefox ; zip -r ../flvideoreplacer.xpi * ; cd ..

2. Uninstall a former version of flvideoreplacer in firefox.

3. Open the created file flvideoreplacer@trupf.xpi in
   firefox to install the extension.